<div style="height:30px; font-weight:bold; font-size:16px; margin-bottom:10px; clear:both;">
<h2><span style="float:left;">英文译文</span></h2>
<a style="float:left; margin-top:7px; margin-left:5px;" href="javascript:PlayFanyi(206)"><img id="speakerimgFanyi206" src="/img/speaker.png" / alt="" width="16" height="16"/></a>
<span id="fanyiPlay206" style=" display:none;width:1px; height:1px; float:left;"></span>
</div>
黄鸟 Yellow Birds<br />黄鸟黄鸟， Yellow birds,listen to me!<br />无集于谷， Don’t cluster on my paper mulberry tree.<br />无啄我粟。 Or eat up my millet completely.<br />此邦之人， People of this land<br />不我肯谷。 Me no food grant<br />言旋言归， All the time I long<br />复我邦族。 to return to my hometown.<br />黄鸟黄鸟， Yellow birds,
